Hotel Billing App (Android Studio Build Guide)

1. Open Android Studio
2. Click "Open an new project"
3. select main.java file and paste it 
3.1 slect xml.main file then paste it on a layout page
4. Let Gradle sync finish
5. Click "Run" or "Build APK"
6. Install the APK file on your phone 
7.if code shows try to connecting a mobile and then download
